snippet.title: Paranoia Movie Trailer OFFICIAL! Liam Hemsworth and Amber Heard Sex Scenes!
snippet.description:
Full Paranoia official movie trailer! Liam Hemsworth and Amber Heard sex scenes, Harrison Ford, Gary Oldman, and more!

http://Twitter.com/ClevverNews - Follow Us!
http://Twitter.com/HerNameIsDeidre - Send Deidre a Tweet!
http://Facebook.com/ClevverNews - Like Us!
http://Clevver.com - Visit our site!
I've got your first look at the trailer for Paranoia!
Liam Hemsworth gets down and dirty (literally and figuratively) in the new trailer for Paranoia, and OMG, it looks amazing.
Check out the intense thriller's trailer, and stay tuned for more details.
Intense, right!?
As you saw, Liam Hemsworth is the main character in the movie—he plays Adam Cassidy, a blue collar worker who's desperate to help his sick dad.
He gets twisted into a dark world of corporate greed, where he's hired by Gary Oldman's character to find out secrets about Harrison Ford's character. Before he knows it, Liam's character is caught in the middle of a high-stakes war between both guys.
Amber Heard plays Liam's love interest, and judging by the steaminess we saw in the trailer, we're gonna see a good amount of sexy time throughout the film.
Paranoia will explode into theatres on August 16th.
Take it the comments section now and let me know if you'll be seeing Paranoia this summer, and if you think this could be Liam best movie yet!?
Remember to SUBSCRIBE to ClevverNews because it's the freakin weekend and you have not only Rumor Patrol coming your way today, but also SHOUT IT OUT tomorrow! Yes, just a reminder, Shout It Out is now airing on Saturdays!
Have a great weekend you guys, and I'll see ya later!
I'm Deidre Behar, you're watching ClevverNews, and I'll see you tomorrow.
